svg.text: Applewood Smoked Pulled Pork Burger $9.49 Tender roasted pork with a fresh apple slaw and choice of side.Reef Burger $9.49 Fresh ground chuck, choice of cheese, maple bacon, lettuce, tomato and onion, served on a fresh baked toasted bun.Garlic Parmesan Burger $9.49 Garlic and parmesan cheese, lettuce, tomato and onion served on a fresh baked toasted bun.Grilled Chicken Club $9.49 On sourdough bread with grilled chicken, bacon, lettuce, tomato, avocado and cheese.Jumbo Kosher dog $6.99Grown-ups Grilled Cheese $7.49
Sandwiches served with choice of fries, chips, salad or a fresh fruit cup.

Strawberry Pecan Salad $8.99 Fresh spring greens, fresh strawberries, candied pecans, blue cheese strawberry vinaigrette and grilled chicken.Chop Cobb Salad $8.99 Chopped mixed greens, bacon, tomatoes, cheddar, eggs, grilled chicken, and choice of dressing.Apple, Blueberry, Bacon Salad $8.99 Blueberries, fresh apples, diced maple bacon, grilled chicken breast, pecans, spring greens and local honey drizzle. Caesar Salad $7.99 Romaine and fresh dressing tossed with parmesan cheese and topped with grilled chicken and fresh made croutons.
